However, if a terminal operation (such as `toList()`) is used right after `asSequence()`, this doesn't give
you any positive performance effect.

**Example:**


      fun test(list: List<String>) {
          list.asSequence().last()
      }

After the quick-fix is applied:


      fun test(list: List<String>) {
          list.last()
      }

